{
  "stem": "10162.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So-- and she left with the baby and my grandmother and my aunt and my little six-year-old cousin.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My aunt had a six-year-old child.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And, and I never ever seen them-- seen them again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You know, then we went.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We marched quite a while.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I remember going through this gate which says 'Arbeit macht frei,' while I still thought we were going to a labor camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then we were going to go through a, a long line where they shaved us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Yeah, oh, but first, we have to-- we had to-- we went into a large hall where we were waiting.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then they said, take off your-- take every-- take off everything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I had a coat on that was a brand new coat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I got that coat a couple of months prior to that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I had it-- my mother had made for me because that was supposed to be more like a big girlish coat.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so we were supposed to not wear it until the fall.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when we left, my mother said, put that on and your best shoe and everything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, how come?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When we left our apartment-- I'm going back there in a little bit.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she said, well, it's because we-- you never know what you will have left with.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I want the best-- you wear the best.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I had this coat that I was so proud of because it had a line that little girls didn't wear.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so they said, take-- take off-- take-- put everything on the floor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I took off this coat and I was looking where I can hang it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I saw some kind of a knob kind of a thing in the wall.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
